Conclusions
• Good place to learn new technologies
• You generate new ideas by learning and associating 
with your own expertise
• Many people around
• Possibility of solving your own questions
• Lots of contacts to do
• How much was it?: it was for free!
• They even provided you accommodation in a hostel (in 
dorms, 1 metro station away)
• Breakfast, lunch, social dinner and some beers included
